Get ready to change how you watch things with our new video player. 

* New forward and back 10-second buttons make it easy to jump to the exact point you want to. Pro-tip: double-tap on the left or right side of the screen while watching to instantly go forward or back.
* Enjoy bigger controls like play/pause, with labels to quickly select Episodes or turn on Audio & Subtitles. 
* Tap the new “Next Episode” button to get to the next one even faster.
